Description: Tools and functions for managing the download of binary
    files.  Binary repositories are defined in 'YAML' format. Defining new
    pre-download, download and post-download templates allow additional
    repositories to be added.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://docs.ropensci.org/binman/, https://github.com/ropensci/binman
